\ STACK OVERFLOW version of ?DO  Very fat.

: ?DO ( -- DO-SYS )
  POSTPONE 2DUP  POSTPONE =
  POSTPONE IF    POSTPONE 2DROP
  POSTPONE ELSE
  POSTPONE DO  [ ' THEN ] LITERAL
; IMMEDIATE

: DO    ( -- DO-SYS )  POSTPONE DO  ['] PAUSE ; IMMEDIATE
: LOOP  ( DO-SYS -- ) >R POSTPONE LOOP  R> EXECUTE ; IMMEDIATE
: +LOOP ( DO-SYS -- ) >R POSTPONE +LOOP R> EXECUTE ; IMMEDIATE
